desc: I make sculptures out of upcycled and recycles silverware and old barbwire and other rustic bits and pieces. They are one off as they are never quite the same. I am happy to work with you to make your own special gift for a loved one. Rustic stunning and completely unique.

layout.text: Unique handmade sculptures and wreaths made from upcycled silverware , barbwire and other recycled bits and pieces
